  %% Diagram 71: Backup, Restore, and Disaster Recovery Flow

  Schedule[Scheduled backup job]
  Create[Create encrypted backup\nPostgreSQL + event store snapshots]
  Verify[Integrity verification]
  Valid{Backup valid?}

  Store[Store backup in retention chain]
  Catalog[Update immutable backup catalog and retention policy]
  Drill[Periodic restore rehearsal]
  Restore[Restore to isolated recovery environment]
  Validate[Recovery validation\nDB consistency + event replay smoke checks]
  Measure[Measure RTO/RPO]
  Meets{RTO/RPO targets met?}

  Fallback[Fallback to previous valid backup chain]
  Incident[Open DR incident and escalate]
  Improve[Update DR runbook and controls]

  Schedule --> Create --> Verify --> Valid
  Valid -- Yes --> Store --> Catalog --> Drill --> Restore --> Validate --> Measure --> Meets
  Valid -- No --> Fallback --> Incident

  Meets -- Yes --> Improve
  Meets -- No --> Incident --> Improve
